    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                <i class="fas fa-venus"></i> What's My Body Type?
            </div>
            <h1>Discover Your Body Shape</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Understanding your body shape is the first step to finding clothes that make you feel yourself, amazing and fabulous...</p>
        </header>
        
        <section class="intro">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-gem"></i> Discover Your Perfect Fit</h2>
            <p>Unlock your shape with our quick calculator. Knowing your body type helps you choose clothes that highlight your best features and make you feel confident.</p>
            <p>Let's get your quick measurements (in centimeters)...</p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="measurement-guide">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-tape"></i> How to Measure Correctly</h2>
            
            <div class="measurement-step">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler body-shape-icon"></i> Chest/Bust</h3>
                <p>The circumference measured around the chest over the fullest part of the breasts, while wearing a properly fitted bra.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="measurement-step">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler body-shape-icon"></i> Waist</h3>
                <p>The smallest circumference measured around the natural waist, just above the belly button.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="measurement-step">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler body-shape-icon"></i> High Hip</h3>
                <p>The circumference of the upper swell of the hip over the pelvic region. It is around 7 inches (18 cm) below the natural waist.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="measurement-step">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler body-shape-icon"></i> Hip</h3>
                <p>The largest circumference measured around the hips over the largest part of the buttocks.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="calculator">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Enter Your Measurements</h2>
            
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="chest">Chest/Bust Size (cm):</label>
                <input type="number" id="chest" placeholder="Enter chest measurement in centimeters" min="60" max="150" step="0.1">
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="waist">Waist Size (cm):</label>
                <input type="number" id="waist" placeholder="Enter waist measurement in centimeters" min="50" max="140" step="0.1">
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="highHip">High Hip Size (cm):</label>
                <input type="number" id="highHip" placeholder="Enter high hip measurement in centimeters" min="60" max="150" step="0.1">
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="hip">Hip Size (cm):</label>
                <input type="number" id="hip" placeholder="Enter hip measurement in centimeters" min="70" max="160" step="0.1">
            </div>
            
            <div class="buttons">
                <button id="calculateBtn"><i class="fas fa-magic"></i> Calculate My Body Type</button>
                <button id="resetBtn"><i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Reset</button>
