        <section class="results" id="results">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> Your Body Type Results</h2>
            <div class="body-type" id="bodyTypeResult">
                <!-- Results will be displayed here -->
            </div>
            
            <div class="tips-toggle">
                <button id="tipsToggleBtn"><i class="fas fa-tshirt"></i> Show Styling Tips for My Body Type</button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="styling-tips" id="stylingTips">
                <!-- Styling tips will be displayed here -->
            </div>
            
            <div class="general-tips" id="generalTips">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> General Styling Tips</h3>
                <div class="tips-content">
                    <p><strong>Fit is Key:</strong> Clothes that fit properly always look better than too tight or too loose. Find clothing that skims your body without clinging.</p>
                    <p><strong>Layering:</strong> Use layers to add shape, such as jackets or cardigans that can define the waist.</p>
                    <p><strong>Color Blocking:</strong> Experiment with color blocking to draw attention to certain areas of the body or balance proportions.</p>
                    <p><strong>Accessories:</strong> Belts can help define the waist and add interest to outfits, while scarves or statement jewelry can draw attention to the face and upper body.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <footer>
            <p><strong><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> What's My Body Type?</strong> | Your Personal Body Shape Calculator</p>
            <p>Remember: All bodies are beautiful. This tool is meant to help you find clothes that make you feel confident and comfortable.</p>
